Back to school today.Yea schools school thats all I have to say.
Didnt really do anything yet. Probably going out later. I'll let you know.

<marquee>Happy new year</marquee>
My new year was exciting. Went out last night. Didnt really drink. I was being good..haha. I was probably the only one who didn't. Had to watch my little cousin today. Then hung out with karen. Watched Family Guy. Thats all I do. Either that or go to Local concerts. There is alot of good conerts around here, its a pretty big city. I love living in the city. It is so full of things to do. You are rarely bored.
But lately i've been getting tired of the city. Seeing the same things over and over again. Oh well I usually have something to do, if not I'll find something.
Happy New year..yay
♥

Yea so today, went shopping. Got sugarcult cd. Thats really it. Hung out with Karen. 
Tomorrow Im not aloud to use my car it needs to go in the shop. My tail lights are broken and i got pulled over for them. So im not aloud to drive it til it gets fixed. Yea that sucks. Oh well.
Watching family guy. I fuckin love that show. ♥
On another note I need to get my digital camera working then i'll post some pics.
